Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到惠梦以前
